donations.donation_comment: THANK YOU CANADIAN TRUCKERS FOR STANDING UP FOR FREEDOM FOR ALL!!  THE WORLD IS WATCHING! GOD BLESS!
Continue to spread liberty and freedom throughout the land.
Blessed Are Those who Hunger and Thirst for Righteousness

God bless all the Truckers and their families.  Their wheels keep our homes going.  Keep on Truckin'!!! You are making an impact on this Fascist undertaking on all Free people everywhere. " We the people" are with you and pray for you each day.  Let Freedom Ring!!!

Holy Spirit FIRE is fighting tyranny on your behalf-- gOH CANADA!!          2Corinthians 4:8-9
New International Version
8 We are hard pressed on every side,(A) but not crushed; perplexed,(B) but not in despair; 9 persecuted,(C) but not abandoned;(D) struck down, but not destroyed.(E)/  Hold the line Truckers-Victory is yours!
donations.donation_name: Much Love from United States of America

donations.donation_comment: Thank you Canadians for leading the world to freedom
Thank you - you’re not only helping your fellow Canadians you are helping the entire world.

Dear Canadians,
Most of us in the USA support your fight for Freedom! We stand with you.   We are having our own issues with our uncaring failed government and the Freedom Convoy gives all Freedom loving peoples around the world hope that this nightmare and government over reach will finally end!  God Bless you in your fight,
Gary & Renee Eagle, Idaho USA
